Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnCalibri\fs28\b1\c&H45A1FF&}Preložila:Momo-chan \N{\c&HAED5FD&}Korektúra: Saya-chin
